            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿وَكَم مِّن مَّلَكٖ﴾: وَكَثِيرٍ مِنَ الملائِكَةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "53:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿تَسۡمِيَةَ ٱلۡأُنثَىٰ﴾: صِفَةَ الأُنْثَى، وهي أَن يُقَالَ لَها: بِنْتٌ.</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "53:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿ٱلظَّنَّ﴾: التَّوهُّمَ الباطِلَ.</h2>\n<h2>﴿لَا يُغۡنِي﴾: لا يُجدِي ولا يَقُومُ مَقَامَ الحَقِّ.</h2>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "53:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>...</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "53:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿مَبۡلَغُهُم مِّنَ ٱلۡعِلۡمِ﴾: مُنْتَهى عِلْمِهِم، لَا عِلْمَ لَهُم فَوْقَهُ؛ والمرادُ ظَنُّهُم الفاسِدُ.</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "53:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿بِٱلۡحُسۡنَى﴾: بالجنَّةِ.</h2>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "53:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>﴿ٱللَّمَمَ﴾: الذُّنُوبَ الصِّغارَ الَّتِي لا يُصِرُّ صاحِبُها عَلَيها، أو يُلِمُّ بِها على وَجْهِ النُّدْرَةِ.</p>\n<p>﴿أَنشَأَكُم مِّنَ ٱلۡأَرۡضِ﴾: خَلَقَ أباكُم آدمَ مِن تُرابٍ.</p>\n<h2>﴿فَلَا تُزَكُّوٓاْ أَنفُسَكُمۡ﴾: فَتَمْدَحُوها بالتَّقْوَى.</h2>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "53:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "ar_muyassarwm",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<h2>﴿تَوَلَّىٰ﴾: أَعْرَضَ عَن طَاعَةِ اللهِ.</h2>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "53:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 109,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Ar Muyassarwm",
